## Lighting Pattern

This scene must be used as lighting evidence.

Top-level light/profile components include `Врезной профиль для подсветки` and nested `Подсветка врезного профиля`, `light_diffuser`, `4000k`, `5000k`, `6000k`, `7000k` variants.

Main kitchen lighting/profile positions:

- Back-wall under-upper profile: `Врезной профиль для подсветки`, bbox approx `X[32..2041] Y[-97.7..120] Z[1310..1514]`, length about 2005mm.
- Left-leg under-upper profile: `Врезной профиль для подсветки#1`, bbox approx `X[-17.7..200] Y[-1664..-30] Z[1310..1514]`, length about 1630mm.
- Right open-shelf/tall feature profile: `Врезной профиль для подсветки#2`, bbox approx `X[2066.6..2284.3] Y[-231.7..-27.7] Z[121.8..2709.8]`, vertical run about 2584mm.

Detached block also contains multiple lighting profile instances; separate them from main-kitchen lighting during verification.

Technical implication for templates: lighting is not only visual render setup. It is a componentized furniture/accessory system with profile body, diffuser, LED strip/temperature options, and placement relative to upper modules or open shelving.

